{"tid":2008463,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"女神崩壞　本田翼自認留家抗疫食肥咗","createTime":"2020-05-09T05:11:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T14:55:33.000Z","uid":16659,"like":88,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"caeab3f6cd1cacfb004df3d2efc08063327d0bee","tid":2008463,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T05:11:48.000Z","msg":"27歲日本女星本田翼，一向以靚樣及甜美笑容獲封宅男女神，近年她開設視頻平台頻道更大受歡迎，至今訂閱人數已超過192萬。<br />\n<br />\n近排因疫情不用開工的她，頻頻在家拍短片更新。昨日她上載新片回答網民提問，有網民唔客氣問她是否因留家抗疫而發福時，臉頰越來越脹的她，無奈尷尬點頭承認。<br />\n<br />\n本田翼年初成為人氣節目《Guruguru 99》美食環節新成員後，已因經常在節目「食好西」而被指發福不少，近排更因日日留家打機，令臉上脂肪有增冇減。不過，本田翼一於少理，邊拍片邊大擦親自炮製的滷水豬腩飯。"},{"pid":"3b41b0204eb9e248d4bdf7ee51929fb007d4d24b","tid":2008463,"uid":16659,"like":21,"dislike":3,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T05:11:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200509/photo/bkn-20200509113122933-0509_00862_001_01p.jpg?20200509114331\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200509%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200509113122933-0509_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20200509114331&h=92cfe58f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d4e6b8b1ed818a881016a7371f832a3fe744cd4","tid":2008463,"uid":16659,"like":101,"dislike":2,"score":99,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T05:12:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200509/photo/bkn-20200509113122933-0509_00862_001_02p.jpg?20200509114331\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200509%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200509113122933-0509_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20200509114331&h=cad14ca7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有網民唔客氣，留言問她是否因留家抗疫而發福。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200509/photo/bkn-20200509113122933-0509_00862_001_03p.jpg?20200509114331\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200509%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200509113122933-0509_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20200509114331&h=4bf42980&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本田翼無奈尷尬點頭承認。"},{"pid":"71eaaa46d7609f99aceac26a159d5471ff0e5f7e","tid":2008463,"uid":16659,"like":76,"dislike":3,"score":73,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T05:13:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200509/photo/bkn-20200509113122933-0509_00862_001_04p.jpg?20200509114331\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200509%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200509113122933-0509_00862_001_04p.jpg%3F20200509114331&h=7aec1ef7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一於少理繼續食！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200509/photo/bkn-20200509113122933-0509_00862_001_05p.jpg?20200509114331\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200509%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200509113122933-0509_00862_001_05p.jpg%3F20200509114331&h=fbc97bd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁食法，想唔肥都難！"},{"pid":"86183785dc6629281bf25e8f1a1e0f2b906e7de1","tid":2008463,"uid":16659,"like":92,"dislike":3,"score":89,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T05:13:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200509/photo/bkn-20200509113122933-0509_00862_001_06p.jpg?20200509114331\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200509%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200509113122933-0509_00862_001_06p.jpg%3F20200509114331&h=a3d7d2f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本田翼早前參演美食節目已經被指發福。"},{"pid":"d30d245bc3ef4205028fefc365ab6a04450a7d21","tid":2008463,"uid":115700,"like":45,"dislike":2,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T05:15:40.000Z","msg":"唔係 本田岬 肥就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70c2a6895c17628c26e6679a0c9c33bbef89c5ad","tid":2008463,"uid":16659,"like":41,"dislike":3,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T05:15:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200509/photo